title: Rounded sans serif
content:
Hi...

Can anyone tell me what font this is?

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150419204910im_/http:/typophile.com/files/cc_6320.jpg)
author: peterboruplund

comments.content: Can be wrong but to me, type on left is not rounded, rather blurred and softened by a screen effect. For the rest, it could be [Alternate Gothic](http://web.archive.org/web/20150419204910/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/urw/alternate-gothic) (No 2). You might like too [Ultramagnetic](http://web.archive.org/web/20150419204910/http:/www.youworkforthem.com/product.php?sku=T0020), [Brauer Neue](http://web.archive.org/web/20150419204910/http:/lineto.com/The+Fonts/Font+Categories/Text+Fonts/Brauer+Neue), [Vinyl](http://web.archive.org/web/20150419204910/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/t26/vinyl)
